days=['Mon','wed','fri']
fruits=['banana','apple']
drinks=['beer','cocktail','vodka']
desserts=['cake','cookie','tea','ice cream']
for day,fruit,drink,dessert in zip(days,fruits,drinks,desserts):
	print(f'In this {day}, I drink {drink} eat {fruit} and {dessert}')


>>In this Mon, I drink beer eat banana and cake
>>In this wed, I drink cocktail eat apple and cookie

zip會在最短的list結束時結束
